name: Akaname
description:
Akanname is a ghost that appears in Japanese folklore.
Generally Akaname shaped like a frog and has a long tongue that sticks out.
The feet have fingers with sharp claws, sometimes described as having dull red or green skin.
Akanname will appear in houses that have dirty and unkempt bathrooms.
They appear at night licking the dirt in the bathroom until clean
